# Lead Search & Geography Rules

## Geographic Selection

- Geography is strictly limited to **ZIP code polygons** and **County Clusters**.
- No radius search or free-hand polygon drawing is allowed (per Tech Doc Section 3.2).

## Data Axle Integration

- Use the **People Dataset** (Consumer) only.
- Mandatory Filters: Geography, Profession (if B2C access confirmed), Net Worth, Age, Recently Moved.
- All lead counts displayed to the user MUST be anonymized and masked (PII protection).

## Performance

- Frontend requests to the search API must be **debounced**.
- Use **Redis caching** for repeated search queries to save Data Axle API credits.
